{"tid":2370504,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"831銅鑼灣，陳姓手足暴動罪成，判處4年監禁","createTime":"2021-01-18T05:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T09:43:12.000Z","uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a291d731c24bbb34f2125a953cba9823cdde22","tid":2370504,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:43:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12982&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=e18ac29c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12982</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第廿八庭 <br />\n#姚勳智法官 #判刑<br />\nD1: 陳(24) #0831銅鑼灣<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n① 暴動<br />\n被控於2019年8月31日在銅鑼灣記利佐治街1號一帶，連同其他參與 #暴動。<br />\n② 無牌管有無線電通訊器具<br />\n被控於同日同地無牌管有一個 #無線電 通訊器具。<br />\n<br />\n陳手足就所面對的兩項控罪，經審訊後在2020年12月28日被姚勳智法官裁定罪名成立，還押索取背景報告，今日處理求情及判刑。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n🙇&zwj;♂️求情<br />\n潘熙資深大律師早前已經呈上書面求情大綱，不在庭上重覆。希望法庭在判刑時不考慮被告在2013年曾經因販運危險藥物被判入教導所。被告品格良好、樂於助人、熱心服務社會，協助區議員派發防疫物資，亦有參與聖約翰救傷隊，今次在錯誤時間出現在錯誤地方。<br />\n<br />\n邀請法庭考慮被告在案中角色、罪責相對地低，身上沒有任何攻擊性武器，亦無安排、帶領、煽惑、鼓動在場示威者，並非激烈示威者。無任何證據證明被告有作出任何暴力行為，亦沒有警員因被告的行為而受傷。<br />\n<br />\n綜上，本案案情嚴重性比DCCC901/2016莫嘉濤案輕，希望法庭考慮被告的良好品格、家庭背景，以3年作為控罪的量刑起點。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n📌判刑理由大綱：<br />\n就本案而言，暴動顯然不是突然發生，約有300人參與暴動，規模龐大。示威者霸佔馬路、部份人身穿護甲、頭盔，手執長形狀物體，也有人縱火焚燒雜物、向警員投擲汽油彈、用雷射筆照射，為時半個多小時，甚具威脅性。以此背景而言，可判處5年或以上監禁。暴動嚴重性不單在被告其個人，而在整個群體所做的事情。 <br />\n<br />\n可幸被告在案中不是帶領角色、亦沒有人因此而嚴重受傷。暴動罪以4年半作量刑起點，考慮被告的個人背景，審訊時承認了大部份控方案情節省法庭時間資源，再減刑半年。此外沒有其他減刑理由。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n🛑各項控罪判刑如下：<br />\n控罪①暴動 4年即時監禁<br />\n控罪②罰款$5,000 (一個月內交)"},{"pid":"9fdf949718f36f190196d232b1eaba7fd23ede5f","tid":2370504,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b3ffcdd4db5aae154e6c824894c733d912750b","tid":2370504,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f6531598b0fb794119f57bce52377aa78bc923","tid":2370504,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2b3d06c3679a89932218846d86b676129d70a9","tid":2370504,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5737c3b8f3b461b4f6e12b09c07dd78973f646e","tid":2370504,"uid":183844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"著護甲都要出嚟<br />\n咪反證知道現場極高危險都要出嚟<br />\n咪即係暴政驅使囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e213bfbed9ec73214b00032c0d2af71baff824","tid":2370504,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:51:26.000Z","msg":"CLS 咁都4年"},{"pid":"b4f396f32106b91475f21972a662badbd494dbeb","tid":2370504,"uid":183844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5737c3b8f3b461b4f6e12b09c07dd78973f646e","tid":2370504,"uid":183844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"著護甲都要出嚟<br />\n咪反證知道現場極高危險都要出嚟<br />\n咪即係暴政驅使囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"個邏輯好撚戇鳩<br />\n假定一班警察(無係講香港嗰啲 嗰啲叫死黑警)追捕一個犯<br />\n最後5個喺不同方向開槍射死佢 死因係身中5彈<br />\n可否話原因係因為佢匿喺一個障礙物後面 所以槍殺佢?<br />\n個邏輯九唔搭八<br />\n重點防具係保護自己<br />\n衫都係防具㗎<br />\n鞋絕對係添啦<br />\n你唔一樣一樣數?<br />\n要入都入有武器喺手啦"},{"pid":"bd786adcb4b7e951e2223044da93a17dfe85f7f2","tid":2370504,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:56:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"289f0d90a0c2b7abca56a862a338bf80ac27733f","tid":2370504,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:03:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"457e30978add86e9b142356bc49cdabb306cdbba","tid":2370504,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:04:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38caf5c3b1a76906ebd789be8010760720934b4b","tid":2370504,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:07:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"871a7eb3b87e5811b8b2c730155c2d7889c229b6","tid":2370504,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:16:41.000Z","msg":"火魔暴動，無計"},{"pid":"bae747169d1e7d1502ca6431f4dc76cbf098a992","tid":2370504,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:18:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">小心認真就輸了呢條五毛</span>"},{"pid":"ee1d988fdee31004e0cd403e245037653005cd94","tid":2370504,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"871a7eb3b87e5811b8b2c730155c2d7889c229b6","tid":2370504,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:16:41.000Z","msg":"火魔暴動，無計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:23:53.000Z","msg":"係革命一定有犧牲有流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尊重手足決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12eab67bb50f629627f6733fc248d5da229420f","tid":2370504,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815f38d5c23fb5d6c426e5db36a759e4e2ba8cc8","tid":2370504,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:33:38.000Z","msg":"好明顯急救員<br />\n<br />\n上訴啦屌"},{"pid":"767ea188ec551f14aa779b7e21e140d378d18dea","tid":2370504,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:46:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a4aeff2ac4aeb59fe82eec6ade0208156f30418","tid":2370504,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e857864f8c8abe1adaafb42dc0aa885f96546a0b","tid":2370504,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"法官姚勳智早前裁決指，首被告陳佐豪案發時有整全防衛裝備認為他當時逃走必因畏罪，加上其夥伴攻擊警方等，難以接納辯方指他為救護員，指他必然曾參與暴動，裁定他暴動及一項無牌管有無線電通訊器罪罪名成立。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/8-31-%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-25-%E6%AD%B2%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E5%B7%A5%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-4-%E5%B9%B4-%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%A5%E7%B4%8D%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%98%AF%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E5%93%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-31-%25E9%258A%2585%25E9%2591%25BC%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-25-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-4-%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25B4%258D%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=9ab4f795\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-31-%25E9%258A%2585%25E9%2591%25BC%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-25-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-4-%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25B4%258D%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%2F&h=b060a2d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/8-31-%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-25-%E6%AD%B2%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E5%B7%A5%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-4-%E5%B9%B4-%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%A5%E7%B4%8D%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%98%AF%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E5%93%A1/</a>"},{"pid":"d2797eef876302abcf066899ff6cb0f3f4bcd7fd","tid":2370504,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbed2d9e2eb0f3cae92474955cfea28c11aa05d","tid":2370504,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"重覆返上次post<br />\n<br />\n1. 辯方證人供詞對手足不利 (話佢急救物資不足, 冇紅藥水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又冇反光衣)<br />\n2. 有人救FA手足, 令個官懷疑係同黨(勇武手足)救佢<br />\n3. 影到佢同黑衣人一齊移動(但冇做任何野)<br />\n4. 未證實到手足離開同前面FA關係(辯方指可能係同前面FA一齊進行救助)<br />\n5. 冇任何人受手足幫助記錄<br />\n<br />\n由於佢身份存疑(大話), 佢又成身護甲<br />\n就屈入左"},{"pid":"d5dd79eadca22d9d3383df1235cc4e4235faac96","tid":2370504,"uid":334183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:42:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"76fb8df4c340d0c811c11c05b99831dcda5799bb","tid":2370504,"uid":334183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:43:12.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}